comments.body:
I think it would be a useful feature to directly import my OCI-format images into containerd for use by Kubernetes. After briefly looking at the containerd source code, using the `containerd.sock` file to connect to containerd seems like a feasible approach.

I'd like to try implementing a `containerd-daemon` transport to support operations on containerd images. I currently don't have development experience with the relevant components, and it looks like it could be a significant effort, so it would likely take considerable time to implement. If you also think this is a good idea, I am willing to provide a PR to support this feature.

@rhatdan @mtrmac
